        "uco-role:Role"
      ],
      "uco-core:name": "SE Enterprise role: residential burglar",
      "uco-core:description": "Residential burglars ('IRL (in real life) Break-in members') targeted hardware virtual currency wallets in victims' homes. Source: PACER Doc 245 (redacted; unredacted Doc 229 returned 2025-10-29) (indictment_ss), paras. 25-26, 16, 32",
