      "uco-core:name": "Marlon Ferro \u2014 Count 1: RICO Conspiracy",
      "uco-core:description": "Knowingly and intentionally conspiring to violate 18 U.S.C. \u00a7 1962(c) \u2014 to conduct and participate in the conduct of the affairs of the SE Enterprise through a pattern of racketeering activity (18 U.S.C. \u00a7\u00a7 1961(1), (5)) consisting of multiple acts indictable under the eight enumerated statutory categories, each defendant agreeing that a conspirator would commit at least two acts of racketeering activity. Source: PACER Doc 245 (redacted; unredacted Doc 229 returned 2025-10-29) (indictment_ss), Count One, paras. 34-36 Ferro pleaded guilty 2025-10-17 and was sentenced 2026-05-06 to 78 months' incarceration, 36 months' supervised release, and a $100 special assessment. Source: PACER Doc docket sheet (docket), Defendant (3); sentencing minute entry",
