      "@id": "urn:uuid:debbd989-6c43-58d2-b623-24d38713f9cd",
      "@type": "uco-action:Action",
      "uco-core:name": "Monitor Victim-4's location in real time through his Apple iCloud account",
      "uco-core:description": "In or around July 2024, Lam accessed Victim-4's Apple iCloud account to monitor Victim-4's location in real time in preparation for the break-in. Source: PACER Doc 245 (redacted; unredacted Doc 229 returned 2025-10-29) (indictment_ss), overt act jj",
