      "uco-core:name": "Execute search warrants at Lam's two Miami rental homes",
      "uco-core:description": "On 2024-09-18, FBI agents executed search warrants at Malone Lam's two rental homes in Miami, searching the residences and inventorying evidence (watched remotely by Tangeman through the security camera system). Source: PACER Doc 318 (sentmemo), Statement of Facts",
